---
---
<section class="py-20 bg-brand-600 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Fondo decorativo -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <svg width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <defs>
        <pattern id="grid" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <path d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1"/>
        </pattern>
      </defs>
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid)" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/20 text-white text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-white rounded-full"></span>
      Sin tarjeta de crédito · Configuración en 5 minutos
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-5 text-balance leading-tight">
      Empieza a controlar tu granja avícola hoy
    </h2>

    <p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Más de 500 granjas en Latinoamérica ya usan AviControl para conocer su rentabilidad real y mejorar su producción. Únete gratis.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a
        href="https://app.avicontrol.app/registro"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50 font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-base transition-colors cursor-pointer"
      >
        Crear cuenta gratuita
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/51999999999?text=Hola%2C%20me%20gustar%C3%ADa%20conocer%20m%C3%A1s%20sobre%20AviControl"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border-2 border-white/40 hover:border-white text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-base transition-colors cursor-pointer"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.15 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.06 1.2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.09 8.19a16 16 0 0 0 5.72 5.72l1.26-1.26a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 21 15z"/></svg>
        Hablar por WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
